.TH "sdc_set_global_alpha" 9 "sdc_set_global_alpha" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
sdc_set_global_alpha \- set global alpha blending modes.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" sdc_set_global_alpha
.BI "(struct mx3fb_data *mx3fb "  ","
.BI "bool enable "  ","
.BI "uint8_t alpha "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "mx3fb" 12
mx3fb context.
.IP "enable" 12
boolean to enable or disable global alpha blending. If disabled,
per pixel blending is used.
.IP "alpha" 12
global alpha value.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success or negative error code on failure.
